# ===========================================
# Only Allow Essential Files
# ===========================================
# Core application files (allowed by not being ignored)
# - src/ (source code)
# - docs/ (public documentation and website)
# - data/ (templates, snippets, detection patterns)
# - test/ (test suites)
# - scripts/ (build and utility scripts)
# - bridge/ (CLI bridge - main files only)
# - package.json, tsconfig.json, etc. (configuration)
# - README.md, LICENSE, CONTRIBUTING.md (documentation)
# - .mcp.json, .claude-plugin (integration files)